topic_title:
Amazon S3
      Website Configuration Routing Rules Routing Rule Condition Property

variables.description: Applies this redirect if the error code equals this value in the event of an                   error.
variables.name: HttpErrorCodeReturnedEquals
variables.required: Conditional. You must specify at least one condition                   property.

variables.description: The object key name prefix when the redirect is applied. For example, to                   redirect requests for ExamplePage.html, set the key prefix to                      ExamplePage.html. To redirect request for all pages with the                   prefix docs/, set the key prefix to docs/, which                   identifies all objects in the docs/ folder.
variables.name: KeyPrefixEquals
variables.required: Conditional. You must at least one condition property.
